            <title><![CDATA[【Cheat Sheet】Docusaurus 記錄]]></title>
            <link>https://Shen-Jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings</link>
            <guid>https://Shen-Jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings</guid>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Aug 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[This is my first post on Docusaurus.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>這篇用來當作自己的小筆記，或是如果荒廢多時未更新可以拿來當 cheat sheet。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="文章相關">文章相關<a href="https://shen-jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings#%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 文章相關" title="Direct link to 文章相關" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="新增文章">新增文章<a href="https://shen-jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings#%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 新增文章" title="Direct link to 新增文章" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ol>
<li><code>blog/</code></li>
<li>md 檔最前面要有 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/docs/api/plugins/@docusaurus/plugin-content-blog#markdown-front-matter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">front matter</a></li>
<li><code>npm run start</code> 本地測試，隨改隨見</li>
<li><code>npm run deploy</code>（部署到 Pages）</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>要最快看到實際改動可用無痕</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="front-matter">front matter<a href="https://shen-jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings#front-matter" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to front matter" title="Direct link to front matter" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li><code>slug</code>: 網址路徑（可自訂）</li>
<li><code>authors</code>: 去掉就不會有作者資訊（大頭貼那些）<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>題外話：填入 <code>authors.yml</code> 沒有的作者還會有 deploy error，防呆做挺好的😆</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><code>last_update</code>: 可和 <code>date</code> 區分</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="references">References<a href="https://shen-jing.github.io/en/blog/Docusaurus_settings#references" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to References" title="Direct link to References" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://notes.boshkuo.com/docs/Docusaurus/installation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bosh Kuo</a></li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>Docusaurus</category>
        </item>
